# Fix Transfer Search and Implement Image Slideshow

This plan addresses the non-functional search engine in the transfers section and implements an auto-cycling image feature for vehicles with multiple photos.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The search engine is currently failing due to an undefined variable in the JavaScript filter logic.
> The image galleries will now automatically cycle through photos on the listing cards to provide a more dynamic "premium" feel.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Transfers View (`app/views/transfers/index.php`)

#### [MODIFY] [index.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/transfers/index.php)

- **Fix Search Logic**: Update `runSearch` to use `totalPax` instead of the undefined `pax`.
- **Card UI Update**:
    - Modify `renderTrCard` (PHP) and `buildCard` (JS) to wrap the vehicle image in a container that supports multiple images.
    - If a gallery exists, the card will render all images but only show one at a time.
- **Auto-Cycling Gallery**:
    - Add CSS for cross-fade transitions between vehicle images.
    - Add JS logic to cycle through images in the cards every 3 seconds for vehicles with galleries.
- **Search Robustness**:
    - Ensure partial matches work correctly for both origins and destinations.

## Open Questions

- Should the auto-cycling start only on hover or be always active? (Planned: Always active with a slow pace for better visibility).

